<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">秋日的赛场旌旗猎猎，竞技的激情澎湃涌动。在江西软件职业技术大学2025年第二十届运动会上，经济管理学院的健儿以昂扬之姿踏上赛道、逐梦竞技。他们用速度诠释激情，用力量书写拼搏，将经管学子的风采与精神，镌刻在每一个运动瞬间，奏响了属于经管人的热血风采乐章。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>活力开幕</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175994495.png" alt="1762175994495.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175994495.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176012736.png" alt="1762176012736.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176012736.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176028452.png" alt="1762176028452.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176028452.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176044270.png" alt="1762176044270.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176044270.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176062602.png" alt="1762176062602.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176062602.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">经管方阵整齐划一</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">旗手们高举旗帜，步伐铿锵</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">队员们手持标语，口号响亮</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">他们眼中的坚定与脸上的自信</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">无不彰显着经管人</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">“团结拼搏、笃行致远”的赛场信念。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">运动会正式拉开序幕！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>田赛风采</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">这里是力量与技巧的舞台</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">跳远、跳绳、铅球……</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">运动员们每一次的跳跃与投掷</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">都在挑战自我</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">他们腾空的身影</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">是赛场上最美的弧线</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">他们沉稳的发力</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">展现了力与美的完美结合</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176118593.png" alt="1762176118593.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176118593.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176141294.png" alt="1762176141294.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176141294.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176151254.png" alt="1762176151254.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176151254.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176165966.png" alt="1762176165966.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176165966.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176177082.png" alt="1762176177082.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176177082.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176197351.png" alt="1762176197351.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176197351.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176211969.png" alt="1762176211969.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176211969.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176222476.png" alt="1762176222476.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176222476.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>径赛竞速</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">发令枪响，是心跳的节拍！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">从百米冲刺的迅如闪电</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">到长跑比赛的毅力坚持</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">跑道上演着一幕幕速度与激情</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">观众的呐喊响彻云霄</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">选手的汗水闪耀光芒</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">每一秒都牵动着我们的心弦</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176264366.png" alt="1762176264366.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176264366.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176276521.png" alt="1762176276521.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176276521.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176290234.png" alt="1762176290234.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176290234.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176303437.png" alt="1762176303437.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176303437.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176315927.png" alt="1762176315927.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176315927.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176327892.png" alt="1762176327892.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176327892.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176338057.png" alt="1762176338057.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176338057.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176348229.png" alt="1762176348229.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176348229.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>趣味赛集锦</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">“三人四足”比赛</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">是协作默契的考验</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">绑在一起的脚步同步向前</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">一声声加油将团队的心紧紧凝聚</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">“踢毽子”比赛哨声一响</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">彩毽在脚尖轻盈翻飞</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">选手们屏气凝神、灵活腾挪</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">现场满是专注与喝彩。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">“集体跳绳”的长绳</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">则如彩虹般上下飞舞</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">队员们默契卡点、鱼贯而入</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">步伐与绳速精准契合</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">展现着整齐划一的团队力量。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">此刻，坚持与灵巧是最好的赛场勋章！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176389154.png" alt="1762176389154.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176389154.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176398586.png" alt="1762176398586.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176398586.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176412735.png" alt="1762176412735.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176412735.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176422809.png" alt="1762176422809.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176422809.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176431591.png" alt="1762176431591.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176431591.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176443109.png" alt="1762176443109.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176443109.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176452139.png" alt="1762176452139.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176452139.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176464927.png" alt="1762176464927.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176464927.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176475124.png" alt="1762176475124.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176475124.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176483866.png" alt="1762176483866.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176483866.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">赛场有终点</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">拼搏无止境</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">盛会的帷幕缓缓落下</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">本届运动会至此圆满收官</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">让我们相约下一个秋天</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">再续这场经管学子关于青春与拼搏的篇章！</span></p>